      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric defined; CFD predictions within ±15 % of experimental measurements for RHI at all operating points.",
      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index (RHI) computed from power-law hemolysis model compared against measured NIH values. Maximum deviation 8 % across all five operating points. Acceptance threshold of ±15 % met. Comparison performed at single laboratory temperature; no multi-temperature comparison conducted."
